{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================
  MISC PDP description block. Renders product.description with
  a Copy all affordance (used by buyers re-publishing copy in
  their own stores).

  Description is a guaranteed product field — always render
  the section even if empty (per Jeff: "description is always
  there on the product").

  Inputs:
    - product
  ============================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="misc-pdp__desc" data-misc-copy-source="description">
  <div class="misc-pdp__desc-head">
    <span class="misc-pdp__desc-title">Description</span>
    <button type="button" class="misc-pdp__copy-btn" data-misc-copy="description">Copy all</button>
  </div>
  <div class="misc-pdp__desc-body" data-misc-copy-text>
    {{ product.description }}
  </div>
</div>
